CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 5, 1941, pg. 12 reads: "National Officers, Delegates And Visitors To Debs About Town Confab In Pittsburgh"...center, left to right; Priscilla Jemmo[ns], Boston and Kay Lomax, Boston...- Harris Photos"
TitMainTitle: Priscilla Jemmons and Kay Lomax, wearing fur coats, posed on Loendi Club porch, for Debs About Town conference
